Path: Flags
Content:
``--width, -w {int}``
: The width of the output. Defaults to 1.
``--alignment, -a {string}``
: The alignment of the output. Defaults to Left (Left(l), Right(r), Center(c/m), MiddleRight(cr/mr)).
``--character, -c {string}``
: The character to fill with. Defaults to ' ' (space).
